when the html document is loaded and ready, the contact form element is found by its id and register callback function to the form submit.

the code logic:
1.get the action value through attribute method;
2.insert the image before the submit element;
3.disable the submit elemet;
4.get the data from form and submit the post ajax request;
5.register the success callback of ajax post request.

